QuestData.Title: Keys to the Kingdom
QuestData.Description:
Need weapons for plan. Have good weapons, but locked up. Gnolls leave key in camp--protect weapon cache.
Get pointiest sticks. They have most blood stains.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect the key and use it to open the weapon cache.
QuestData.RewardText:
Always wanted power stick!
MON-ARK PROVIDES!
